{"tid":2285700,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人呢排睇緊禮志?","createTime":"2020-11-14T10:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T11:42:04.000Z","uid":76115,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"140bdf70d377a48eb65437e458750443456f9d02","tid":2285700,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T10:22:55.000Z","msg":"夫人含天地陰陽之靈，有哀樂喜怒之情。乃聖垂範，以為民極，節其驕淫，以防其暴亂；崇高天地，虔敬鬼神，列尊卑之序，成夫婦之義，然後為國為家，可得而治也。《傳》曰：「一日克己復禮，天下歸仁。」若乃太一初分，燧人鑽火，志有暢於恭儉，情不由乎玉帛，而酌玄流於春澗之右，焚封豕于秋林之外，亦無得而闕焉。軒頊依神，唐虞稽古，逮乎隆周，其文大備。或垂百官之範，置不刊之法；或禮經三百，威儀三千，皆所以弘宣天意，雕刻人理。叔代澆訛，王風陵謝，事睽光國，禮亦愆家。趙簡子問太叔以揖讓周旋之禮，對曰：「蓋所謂儀而非禮也。」天經地義之道，自茲尤缺。哀公十一年，孔子自衛反魯，跡三代之典，垂百王之訓，時無明後，道噎不行。晉書「禮志」"},{"pid":"170c6650b843a96e1f5b504c4e9e1e318328108a","tid":2285700,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T10:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3835b18ac87ec0e640f296c7b0db9f0aebdf7aa9","tid":2285700,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"170c6650b843a96e1f5b504c4e9e1e318328108a","tid":2285700,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T10:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T10:28:39.000Z","msg":"睇到你拉我啲post個心有少少痛。"},{"pid":"333ed7f04b1cfc66fd7b54ef6b3d31986c6aee13","tid":2285700,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T10:29:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d82cf8ba1e091eab2e23e68c6a8cdefceeb7ad9","tid":2285700,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3835b18ac87ec0e640f296c7b0db9f0aebdf7aa9","tid":2285700,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"170c6650b843a96e1f5b504c4e9e1e318328108a","tid":2285700,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T10:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" 